    It’s okay, but not quite what I expected.

Reviewed in the United States on May 2, 2020Verified Purchase









    I recently became an Internet radio broadcaster, and this was the headset mic that was recommended to me by several people who have been doing this for awhile.  Music does sound good coming through the headphones, and they’re fairly comfortable.  Mic does sound good...when it stays in one place. That’s my biggest problem.  The arm that attaches the mic to the headset is deliberately flexible so the mic can be moved, but in this case, it’s actually too flexible, to the point where it doesn’t stay in the position I put it in.  When I listen back to my voice breaks, I can hear their quality change because the mic moves position as I’m speaking.  That’s extremely annoying!

