    My favorite stereo headphone with microphone that I've owned

Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2017Verified Purchase









    This USB stereo set is truly excellent. I'm currently using them to write this review using Dragon NaturallySpeaking and even though I lost my voice a couple of days ago the transcription accuracy so far as 100% (Woops 'is' was translated 'as' user corrected).The headphones are very comfortable and the microphone is flexible and adjustable so that it can pick up my voice easily. Some headsets don't have flexible microphones and they are kind of hard and they just stick out, which doesn't make for good sound quality pickup from the microphone piece.This is actually my favorite headset that I've owned out of the three or four different headsets that I've owned. I haven't had any complaints that people can't hear me when I use Google phone to call people and I used to get some complaints here and there. I've also noticed a significant increase in transcription accuracy since using this microphone/headset.

